{"tid":2349611,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得香港人被老屎忽欺壓都係掋死？","createTime":"2021-01-01T16:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T17:54:13.000Z","uid":241093,"like":53,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"53539a2dc3b154fda2483f23ed08744029c7ea3c","tid":2349611,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"1. 年資<br />\n<br />\n姜濤擰我最喜愛男歌手獎就嫌佢年資唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連擰獎都要講年資<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得香港咁多老屎忽成日講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「我年資大過你！食鹽多過你食米<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你無資格教我！<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔肯接受新文化<br />\n<br />\n造型前衛少少 就話人乸型 <br />\n「都唔明點解有人中意佢，唔夠man，以前90年代有肌肉先係靚仔型男」<br />\n而家2021年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時代唔同咗 人人口味都會變<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請接受現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時實年姜濤呢type冧好多女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你見幾多人中意韓仔就知<br />\n<br />\n連登仔最支持男女平等 唔係應該支持男性自決自己風格？<br />\n男性性別定型文化極為嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身對姜濤無感 聽完佢live同haters搞到想變fan屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a0dec16aae741abd5d033be92aed93088e3230","tid":2349611,"uid":87394,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:22:03.000Z","msg":"比佢地反我就放心<br />\n依家姜b既遭遇同當年gd jb個d差唔多<br />\n香港樂壇終於有救"},{"pid":"783ea3f368a9cf2279e6986cd2e8a40326124bab","tid":2349611,"uid":345839,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:24:47.000Z","msg":"等同當年林峰攞最受歡迎男歌手咪又係比人話<br />\n平心而論, 當年的確係佢d歌最受歡迎<br />\n輪公平仲好過方大同突然攞男歌手金獎"},{"pid":"361de867a18e69e6f81a6deaffaf99bfa8b9508f","tid":2349611,"uid":242444,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:26:09.000Z","msg":"因為老屎忽文化<br />\n之前個件雞容年年霸住個獎<br />\n女歌手全部上唔到位"},{"pid":"235a97a74c42a9a3553f9003cfa904acf7bcdeb2","tid":2349611,"uid":241093,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"361de867a18e69e6f81a6deaffaf99bfa8b9508f","tid":2349611,"uid":242444,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:26:09.000Z","msg":"因為老屎忽文化<br />\n之前個件雞容年年霸住個獎<br />\n女歌手全部上唔到位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:28:11.000Z","msg":"所以香港人係心甘情願屈服老屎忽文化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd98ee1cf4a64f2c9c8433765319b49591b257c2","tid":2349611,"uid":360404,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:29:37.000Z","msg":"其實大把連登仔都好老屎忽，成日喺度小朋友小朋友，小朋友呢term真係撚柒"},{"pid":"081438ea3d87af7779386924da04aa51b9945d06","tid":2349611,"uid":22131,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"有新衝擊係好事<br />\n出道幾年就要俾你拎上神枱嘅張國榮張學友比較都痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904a107c2b963cb6bed9c650134e62a2d4c03c40","tid":2349611,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:31:02.000Z","msg":"香港樂壇=馬騮戲<br />\n是但"},{"pid":"b5f4953b6eae2b8f42fe75e60784584122f4fd3e","tid":2349611,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"油頭粉面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2768cc4e5e3648e20a03f5e92e26f55ceac2d8","tid":2349611,"uid":241093,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fd98ee1cf4a64f2c9c8433765319b49591b257c2","tid":2349611,"uid":360404,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":